A group of armed men hit a cash van in Hillbrow Johannesburg on
Thursday afternoon. The incident occurred at Highpoint in Hillbrow next to KFC, on
Pretoria Street. It is alleged that three people were injured in the incident. A police officer reportedly gave chase in a BMW but was shot. “On scene and transporting a critically injured guard and a
civilian following a CIT robbery,” emergency services provider EMER-G-MED
said. 